      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented test suite; ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 release notes confirm regression testing against benchmark cases.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 is a commercially released, version-controlled CFD solver with a documented quality assurance programme. Release validation suite covers rotating machinery and non-Newtonian flow benchmarks relevant to blood pump simulation. Internal configuration management records confirm solver version traceability throughout the study."
