      "rationale": "Validation experiments were performed on the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump — the identical geometry used in the submission simulations — under the five operating points that span the CPB clinical envelope. Blood analogue fluid properties match those used in the CFD model. The validation domain is therefore directly representative of the COU, and no extrapolation beyond the validated operating space is required."
