      "rationale": "At Model Risk Level 2, independent quantification of numerical solver error beyond code verification is not required when a commercially released solver with a documented QA programme is employed. ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 satisfies this condition. This factor is scoped out of the formal assessment consistent with the MRL 2 assessment plan."
